<subSubSection pageId="250" pageNumber="528" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="250.[1450,2658,2304,2927]" pageId="250" pageNumber="528">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1450,1688,2698,2731]" pageId="250" pageNumber="528">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Tapecua Leaf-eared Mouse is nocturnal. Large hindfeet, long tail, and general habitat associated with it suggest thatit could be somewhat arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
